node.text: Success begins as a state of mind. The #G650 family is now 400+ aircraft strong, with 110+ city pair speed records. Keep going. #MondayMotivation

node.text:
ICYMI, every international flight so far has been record-setting for the all-new #G700. After just claiming city-pair speed records en route to Doha and Paris, the aircraft set its third when it returned to Savannah (using #SAF from @JETEX #LeBourget).

7h 59m |  Avg. Mach 0.90 |  Surpassed previous record by 30 minutes

node.text:
#NEWS: The all-new, fully outfitted #G700 set its first two city-pair speed records during its maiden international voyage — Savannah to Doha and Doha to Paris. Carbon offsets are being applied for both flights.

✈️ Savannah to Doha: 6,711 nm/12,428 km | Mach 0.88 | 13h 16m
✈️Doha to Paris: 2,953 nm/5,469 km | Mach 0.90 | 6h 15m

More details at the #linkinbio.
